## Purpose
- Standardize forms using Server Actions, React Hook Form and Zod, with accessible UX and consistent result shapes.

## Rules
- Zod-first schemas in shared package; infer TS types.
- Server Actions handle mutations; return `{ ok, data?, error? }`.
- Client uses RHF + zodResolver; inline errors; aria-live feedback.

## Good result shape
```
{ ok: true, data: {...} }
{ ok: false, error: { code: "VALIDATION", fields: { email: "Invalid" } }}
```

